snippet.title: Island Party | Event Trailer
snippet.description:
Island Party is coming soon with summertime fun in the Land of Dawn.
Adventurers, come and explore Island Treasures, or go on summer vacations with the heroines!
More events await, where you can get Lunox for free, buy Monthly Pass at half price, and find limited skins in Skin Shop!
Tap the video to find out more about Island Party!
Event Begins: 08/26/2022 00:00
